I"Ë<p><em>Extraction</em> (2019) uses grid-based mediation of video to analyse and restructure networks of data mediation inherent in digital life. The increasing fragmentation of social communication blurs the distinction between real and virtual.</p>

<p>The content is subordinated by the gesture in a mediated reality.
Pixel values represent behaviour on an eight-bit scale.</p>

